text: Bishtiryak () is a rural locality (a village) in Baishevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 197 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 116 km from Isyangulovo, 33 km from Baishevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Bishtiryak
